Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:04.54,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Kawajiri residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.83,0:00:05.09,sign_27_1_July_12th__Mon__,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(381,1)}July 16th (Fri)  7:57 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:07.61,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.95,0:00:11.11,JoJo-main,Kawa,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Well done, Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:16.69,JoJo-main,Kaw,0000,0000,0000,,You protected me from that nuisance, Rohan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:19.85,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you that you \Nhave the wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:20.94,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:22.87,JoJo-main,Kawa,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}They had the wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:22.87,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:26.74,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll head to work so I can make
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.74,0:00:29.15,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,my precious family happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:34.91,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,But first, do you mind if \NI give you a goodbye kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:35.59,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.05,0:00:52.28,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! My precious teapot...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.23,0:00:55.53,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:58.57,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I never know what you're thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:01:02.44,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,You never even answer me! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:04.04,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:14.79,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, he's not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.79,0:01:17.45,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,If I say anything about him to anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.45,0:01:20.55,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll be blown away, \Nand the morning will reset.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.55,0:01:23.53,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,If we just keep letting him do what he wants,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:27.48,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,it might not happen now, but he'll \Neventually kill me and my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:44.69,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rohan Kishibe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:47.55,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,There was someone other than \NKira who had abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.55,0:01:49.97,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do something about Rohan Kishibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:52.88,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who can save me \Nand my mom and defeat Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:56.26,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,is someone with abilities like Rohan Kishibe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:03.43,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There he is. It's Rohan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:07.56,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,If I meet Rohan, he'll be \Nblown away and die...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:10.64,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'll repeat the same morning again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:14.69,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I have to tell Rohan about \Nhim without meeting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:16.87,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to change fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.15,0:02:23.27,sign_3337_34_Flip,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(155,1)}Flip
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:24.46,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:24.22,sign_3436_35__Warning_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,[Warning]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:27.79,sign_3458_36__Warning__You_mu,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,[Warning]\NYou mustn't read any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:27.79,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,It's Rohan's ability that he \Nused one me the last morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:30.54,JoJo-main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:36.28,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I was hiding from Rohan this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:38.47,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rohan didn't even see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:44.01,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,Once fate has happened, \Nit can't be changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:47.02,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:08.93,JoJo-MainTitle,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(402,1)}Jojo's Bizarre Adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:08.93,JoJo-MainTitle2,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(402,1)}Diamond is Unbreakable
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.58,sign_27_1_July_12th__Mon__,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,372)}July 16th (Fri)  8:27 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:16.24,JoJo-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ugh, the forecast didn't \Nsay it was going to rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:17.38,JoJo-EpTitle,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(572,605)}Episode 36      {\fs20}Bites the Dust, Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:25.22,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be under the impression that \Nyou purposely broke the teapot,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:26.57,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,but that is incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:31.58,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever broke last morning \Nwill break again, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:34.25,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,It'll happen because it's meant to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:37.72,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,That is what fate is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:40.75,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,If you were turned into a book last morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:42.92,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,you'll turn into a book, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:46.93,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,This is why Deadly Queen \NBites the Dust is invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:50.99,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,It erases my identity and returns \Neverything else to what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:59.13,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,That means I get to observe Rohan\Nexploding before I head to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:03.35,sign_7188_60_It_rained_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,It rained.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:03.35,sign_7188_61_At_8_27_AM___lig,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,At 8:27 AM, \Nlightning struck \Nabove the Pepsi sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:03.36,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let Rohan die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:07.57,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I have to save Rohan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:26.09,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Rohan Kishibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:28.40,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,Watch carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:33.05,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,He has no idea why he's dying right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:39.10,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's thinking about how he \Nwon't be able to draw his manga anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:00.92,JoJo-main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rohan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:07.93,JoJo-main,Rei,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:17.33,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,Hayato, the very fact that you \Nmet Rohan will disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:19.94,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and the morning will continue on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:22.45,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,If I undo Bites the Dust right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:26.77,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Rohan's death will just become \Nfact and not repeat again...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:29.29,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,But for now, I won't undo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:32.45,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,A few of his friends should \Nalso be showing up, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:37.71,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to automatically \Ndefeat them for me, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:40.18,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,Just like a landmine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:47.23,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,But Bites the Dust won't cause you any harm,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:50.85,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,so you should relax and enjoy \Nyour fun life as a young boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:54.97,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have to head to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.13,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you study hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:04.77,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault. It's because he met me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:08.52,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Rohan Kishibe was killed because he met me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:25.12,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Can't I do anything to defeat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:34.26,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:37.17,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what time it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.65,0:07:40.42,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,My watch doesn't seem to be working right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:43.00,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:49.02,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,It's 8:33...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:52.40,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Haven't I seen you somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:54.24,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Where was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:56.45,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.97,0:07:57.87,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:07:59.99,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh... I guess I was imagining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:02.83,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for saying something weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:06.21,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,8:33... Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:10.71,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro! It really is past 8:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:13.84,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Strange, though... I wonder \Nwhere Rohan-sensei went.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:17.32,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're Rohan Kishibe's friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:18.85,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,They were supposed to meet up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:23.08,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}He left the car door wide open \Nand the key in the ignition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:21.24,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,They probably have the same abilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:26.86,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They also came to ask \Nme about Yoshikage Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:25.57,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That's not like Rohan-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:37.40,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! If they find out \Nthat I'm Hayato Kawajiri
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:40.07,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That's Rohan-sensei's earring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:40.07,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,and ask me about my dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:46.31,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:49.14,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I overslept and was late \Nmeeting up with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:52.97,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I've seen you before... Where was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:57.14,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Josuke and Okuyasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.05,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:09:01.10,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Koichi. Good morning, Jotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:05.20,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}What, so Rohan's the only \None who's not here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:03.96,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,A-And two more...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:07.48,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,When he said his friends \Nwere going to show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:11.59,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}We won't know where Hayato Kawajiri's \Nhouse is if he's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:09.39,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,He must have been talking about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.78,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered I accidentally \Ngrabbed onto this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:18.22,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. Your hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:21.04,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:24.09,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,That angle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:28.57,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,It's that angle. I'm sure \NI've seen him before...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:32.55,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Where was it? I know I've seen him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:35.30,JoJo-main,Jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Koichi. Look at the name on his backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.18,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:38.55,sign_13815_126_Hayato_Kawajiri,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Hayato Kawajiri
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:38.55,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Hayato Kawajiri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:40.30,JoJo-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:42.72,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've been found out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.98,sign_14050_131_Wake_up,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.98,sign_14050_132_The_weather_repo,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The weather report begins
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.98,sign_14050_133_Kira_leaves_the_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Kira leaves the house
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.98,sign_14050_134_Hayato_meets_Roh,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Hayato meets Rohan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.98,sign_14050_135_Lightning_strike,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning strikes the Pepsi sign
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.98,sign_14050_136_Rohan_Kishibe_ex,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Rohan Kishibe dies from explosion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.40,sign_27_1_July_12th__Mon__,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,393)}July 16th (Fri)  8:34 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:55.76,JoJo-main,Jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Hayato Kawajiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:58.19,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:09:59.77,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.77,0:10:02.99,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,D-Does this have to do with \NRohan-sensei not being here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:08.39,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,If these four start asking me about my dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:12.00,JoJo-internal/narrator,Hya,0000,0000,0000,,They're all going to be blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:16.26,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! Don't ask me any questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:21.26,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,If you guys die, too, \Nwho's going to defeat him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:24.01,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I have to deceive them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:27.48,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let these people die, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:32.19,JoJo-main,Jojo,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask you about this photo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:37.19,JoJo-main,Jojo,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know why you were \Nrecording a video in this photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.70,JoJo-main,Jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you recording your da—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.78,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,M-My nose is bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:44.99,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go to the clinic! \NMy nose is gushing blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:46.67,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I... Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:47.53,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:51.65,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,Your nose is bleeding? Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:55.75,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,Here. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:59.76,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:02.48,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to go to a clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:06.35,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,Your nose isn't bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:07.27,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:08.75,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:13.15,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Josuke Higashikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:16.23,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,He's a relative of mine, Jotaro Kujo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:19.07,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,The one with the scary face \Nover there is Okuyasu Nijimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:21.99,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,And the friendly-looking \Nguy there is Koichi Hirose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:25.17,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,You go to Budogaoka Elementary, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.17,0:11:27.17,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you won't be late just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:29.00,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,We just have some questions...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:32.00,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,about this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:35.04,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,If it's nothing, then that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:38.96,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, it is something! \NDon't ask me any questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.96,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,You can't ask me any questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:42.68,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,Is the person in this picture
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:44.82,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,your da—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:48.06,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't say any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:53.81,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's no use...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:56.84,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Now they're going to ask even more questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:12:00.26,JoJo-internal/narrator,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "Don't say anymore"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:01.43,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haa,0000,0000,0000,,One after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:03.13,JoJo-internal/narrator,Jojo,0000,0000,0000,,What are we not supposed to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:04.48,JoJo-internal/narrator,Hya,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:06.50,JoJo-internal/narrator,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:07.85,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,They're going to explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:09.54,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,They're all going to explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:12.97,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,You suddenly shouted, "No!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:14.77,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't say any more"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:17.36,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,But we didn't ask you anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:18.55,JoJo-main,Jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:23.08,JoJo-main,Jojo,0000,0000,0000,,that even asking you a \Nquestion is a bad idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:23.15,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}They're going to explode... \NExplode... Explode...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.92,0:12:25.43,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:33.31,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I-If I die, no one else will have to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:36.81,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm the bomb, I just need to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:43.07,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,If I die, I'm sure these people will be \Nable to defeat him and save my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:51.12,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, ask him about \NKosaku Kawajiri already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:54.31,JoJo-main,Jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Josuke. Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.59,0:12:58.82,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,What are you crouching down for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.75,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I-It won't go through...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:08.51,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, the box cutter \Nwon't go into my throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:09.56,JoJo-main,Jojo,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:10.84,JoJo-main,Josu,0000,0000,0000,,That Stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:13.18,JoJo-main,Oku,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never forget it after seeing it once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:14.52,JoJo-main,Koi,0000,0000,0000,,Deadly Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:20.61,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,To be more precise,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:24.38,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,its Deadly Queen's third bomb, Bites the Dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:26.29,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,It's already too late to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:31.58,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're seeing me, that means \NI'm already inside your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:35.58,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how many of you \Nthere are, because all at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:39.59,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to find out my identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:58.98,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're already awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:04.49,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you replied for once when I \Ncalled you, but there's no need to yell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:06.66,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Breakfast is ready, so come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:18.50,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't stop it... \NThose four got attacked, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:22.89,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use... No matter how hard I try,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:28.01,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,in an hour, fate is going to \Neliminate those four, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.89,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:33.02,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,My dying would be troublesome to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:37.10,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,so Bites the Dust must be \Nautomatically protecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:39.38,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,He's too strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:42.14,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshikage Kira is too much of a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:48.56,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Either he has to die, or he has to undo\NBites the Dust for whatever reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:52.18,JoJo-main,Hayya,0000,0000,0000,,or those four are going to die for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:12.30,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Either he has to die, or he \Nhas to undo Bites the Dust...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:20.31,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought there was no \Nway I could ever kill someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:26.53,JoJo-internal/narrator,Hayya,0000,0000,0000,,There was no way an 11-year-old boy \Nlike me could kill a monster like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:29.41,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:33.57,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,A way for an 11-year-old \Nlike me to kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:35.20,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.77,0:15:44.29,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,And it's sleeping quietly in the dark \Nattic like a gun resting in an armory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:50.80,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time in my life, I was praying \Nto God from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:57.21,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,"Lord, please let me kill this man somehow."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:09.72,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:13.46,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,This cat-like plant starts moving \Nwhen sunlight hits it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.46,0:16:16.01,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,and then attacks by shooting air bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:20.08,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,And even with just this little bit of light \Nin the room, it's so destructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:21.32,JoJo-internal/narrator,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,This behavior...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:22.81,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll utilize this behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:26.42,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,and attack him with an \Nair bullet at point blank range.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:29.86,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Point blank range...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:32.30,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,But when and how am I supposed to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:35.39,JoJo-internal/narrator,Hya,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it in or near the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:37.13,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.63,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,That's it... My hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:43.32,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll come to put the hat on my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:46.46,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be point blank range!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:49.52,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,My chance will be when he \Ncomes into range behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.52,0:16:51.53,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I have to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:56.43,JoJo-announcertop,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way! We're on the air already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:59.12,JoJo-announcertop,ANN,0000,0000,0000,,Er, um... It's now 7:55...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:01.98,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Dad was saying that he wanted \Nanother cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:09.71,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:12.34,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,No, you've got the wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:14.66,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the Sakurai residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:26.76,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, darling. Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:29.94,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your fresh cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:37.40,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:39.17,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lovely morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.17,0:17:42.95,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it wouldn't hurt to have \Nanother cup before I go to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:46.96,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Fate doesn't change with \NBites the Dust, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:52.46,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Something that's been destroyed once will be \Ndestroyed, no matter how much I fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:54.59,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,You said that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:01.35,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,My precious tea set!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:03.85,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:08.02,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Mom, I'm heading to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:16.15,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be there for you. \NI'll protect you forever, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:29.95,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:34.76,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,I really never have any idea \Nwhat he's thinking... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.15,0:18:38.76,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's not so bad after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:42.02,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's fine. I'll clean that up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.77,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can \Ndo now that it's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:47.18,JoJo-main,Shin,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, did you get burnt?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:50.30,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,No... I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:58.65,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:03.99,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's not here... He's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.98,0:19:09.37,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,S-Something's wrong. He should have \Nalready been here by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.71,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:13.46,JoJo-main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, the forecast didn't \Nsay it was going to rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:15.59,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's starting to rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.99,0:19:20.84,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Did fate change because I \Nleft the house before him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:23.15,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,No, that can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:25.14,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's coming to put the hat on my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:28.64,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,he should definitely come up from behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:33.15,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lightning struck the Pepsi sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:36.76,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. Calm down! There \Nare still two minutes left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:41.64,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,There's more than two minutes before \NRohan Kishibe is automatically blown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:42.91,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I need to believe in fate—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:53.13,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's already by that tree... \NHe's already right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:59.61,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,What a lovely morning. \NBut Hayato was acting strangely...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:00.88,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.48,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a hunch, \Nbut something was strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:06.66,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that we've repeated this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:09.89,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,three... no, four times now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:12.90,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is he just that intuitive?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:15.40,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:18.28,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to attack him from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:24.78,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did he figure out that \NI have the cat plant,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:27.58,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and that's why he's not coming near me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:30.65,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,No... He's too close if he knows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:35.37,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to completely \Ndefeat him in one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:40.84,JoJo-internal/narrator,Hhaya,0000,0000,0000,,If I miss, Rohan will explode, \Nand then he'll undo Bites the Dust
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:43.77,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,after the other four are eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:46.64,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, he's going to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:48.90,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time! Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:50.60,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more step to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:53.89,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,If he just steps out from \Nbehind that filthy tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.90,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I can attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:21:01.15,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,What?! H-He's hidden himself even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:03.82,JoJo-internal/narrator,Ira,0000,0000,0000,,The look in Hayato's eyes \Nwhen he left the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.42,JoJo-internal/narrator,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,He looked determined about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:11.78,JoJo-internal/narrator,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same look that the loathsome \NKoichi Hirose and shitbag Josuke have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.78,0:21:16.26,JoJo-internal/narrator,Ira,0000,0000,0000,,My hunch is telling me to \Ncarefully observe him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:20.17,JoJo-internal/narrator,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,Though there really isn't \Nmuch that Hayato can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:21.53,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:26.97,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Once it's a few seconds past 8:29, \Nthe attack on Rohan Kishibe will start!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:32.18,JoJo-internal/narrator,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,That brat is shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:37.40,JoJo-internal/narrator,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,Those eyes look like a despaired \Nmouse drowning in a cesspool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:40.90,JoJo-internal/narrator,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was just imagining \Nhis determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:43.28,JoJo-internal/narrator,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,Those are definitely the eyes of a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.31,0:21:45.86,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,He moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:50.66,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,I came to bring the hat you forgot, Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:55.29,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a God, I thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:59.87,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I thank the fate that got this murderer \Nto move from behind that tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:02.71,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a fighting spirit burning within me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:05.39,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, Yoshikage Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:12.87,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:16.48,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.28,0:22:22.48,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I hit him dead-on! I... I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:25.03,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,Hayato Kawajiri's not coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:28.26,JoJo-main,Roha,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he must've taken \Na different route to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:35.12,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end, you murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.18,0:22:42.59,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:45.42,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,Lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:46.59,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:49.30,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,With my nails growing so quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.79,0:22:54.85,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,I got to thinking about how \Nunlucky I've been lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:56.83,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,But inside my pocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.83,0:23:01.86,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like, since last night, \Nluck is coming around to my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.56,0:23:07.40,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,Remember when Mom's precious \Ntea cup broke this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.79,0:23:11.60,JoJo-main,Kra,0000,0000,0000,,When the coffee spilled onto \Nmy wrist, I was burned,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.60,0:23:15.41,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,so I removed my watch and \Nput it in my chest pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.41,0:23:18.06,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,What unbelievable luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.06,0:23:21.67,JoJo-main,Kira,0000,0000,0000,,If that coffee hadn't spilled this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:26.38,JoJo-internal/narrator,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,How... How is that possible? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:28.88,JoJo-main,Haya,0000,0000,0000,,I... I failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.82,0:23:33.56,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's almost time!
